「不可使用謬誤資料或歪曲事實。持牌人亦不應錯誤引導觀眾，以致對節目提及的人士或團體不公平」<br />\n<br />\nTVB在反送中的報導完全扭曲事相，報導嚴重偏袒警方和政府，報導失實 ， 偏頗，例如6月12日的「六點半新聞報道」和「晚間新聞」，完全不播放及不提及：<br />\n1. 警方違法向多名記者開槍，棍打記者<br />\n2. 警方違法瞄準市民頭部發射布袋彈和橡膠子彈<br />\n3. 在沒有任何襲擊下，警方違法向婦孺、伯伯開槍<br />\n4. 警方違法向市民投擲鐵枝、磗頭<br />\n5. 隻字不提一些市民向警方掟水樽垃圾等之前，警方在多處在沒有受到任何襲擊，提出任何警告下，違法突然向市民開槍，不斷發射催淚彈，布袋彈和橡膠子彈，導致局勢快速失控<br />\n6.隻字不提有市民於6月15日於太古廣場因展示示威標語墮樓, 送院搶救後不治的事實<br />\n<br />\n投訴表格：<a href=\"https://apps.coms-auth.hk/apps/broadcasting_complaint/index.aspx?lang=2\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fapps.coms-auth.hk%2Fapps%2Fbroadcasting_complaint%2Findex.aspx%3Flang%3D2&d=q0LkGBAelTJmoxhYCIypyZKhd8YmQljH21R%2F5cbT5WU%3D&h=c504ff05\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://apps.coms-auth.hk/apps/broadcasting_complaint/index.aspx?lang=2</a></strong></span></span><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<strong><span style=\"font-size: large;\"><span style=\"color: green;\">日期： 2019/6/12 時間1830 新聞報導</span></span></strong>"},{"pid":"abd896a0f50a08ce7723c042125ff1e730801f88","tid":1231853,"uid":168366,"like":7,"dislike":0,"score":7,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-16T14:27:27.000Z","msg":"89年油麻地已經試過一次<br />\n<br />\n見到記住影實佢地"},{"pid":"db8144a200669fb0bb4563d145ebf0afe97f890d","tid":1231853,"uid":96945,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-16T14:33:36.000Z","msg":"係咪洞庭湖草頭鄉落黎嘅?"},{"pid":"bc7dd7a8be6824f059cc61597a7c69769425b426","tid":1231853,"uid":258370,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-16T14:35:20.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"e9e1db5059eb0bae0579e7b8c28da86b3b0dab0c","tid":1231853,"uid":262701,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-16T14:36:45.000Z","msg":"屌你老母"},{"pid":"ecc07f04cfdc873f7e92d70a2294257cd6cdf9d7","tid":1231853,"uid":33222,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-16T14:38:56.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/offtopic.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6f0ee56fc43fadc742c3b749c34f6028519cc57d","tid":1231853,"ui